'''Domain Yo'gand''' was an early [[Domain]] among the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. During the [[Cremlevian War]], the Domain, under the leadership of [[Yo'gand]], was one of the most powerful. The Domain engaged in battle with [[Domain Steng]] to see who would rein over the [[Yuuzhan Vong galaxy]]. In the [[Battle of Ygziir]], Yo'gand killed Steng and [[Yo'gand's Core|dropped]] [[Ygziir]]'s [[Moon/Legends|moon]] into it. With Steng dead, Yo'gand assumed the post of [[Supreme Overlord]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]], but the galaxy his Domain had fought for was ruined.

